message.entry: The input must be real-valued, with a built-in floating-point datatype (double or single).
The number of input symbols must be divisible by the length of the InterleaverIndices property.
This mode is not supported for the GPU-based Turbo Decoder.
The InterleaverIndices property must be set to a positive integer vector with unique elements.
The TrellisStructure property must be set to a valid trellis.
The constituent encoder rate must be 1/2, 1/3, or 1/4.
The constraint length must be a positive integer between 2 and 5.
